  "text": "The entire Intrepid system consists of 128 dual-core file servers. The file servers connect to DataDirect 9900 SAN storage arrays through the Infiniband DDR ports, each with a theoretical unidirectional bandwidth of 16 Gbps. All the 128 file servers can theoretically deliver up to 2 Tbps [CITATION_1] .",
